Module com.example.demosudoku
Package com.example.demosudoku.model.game

Interface IGame

All Known Implementing Classes:
Game, GameAbstract, GameAdapter
public interface IGame
Interface defining the contract for game operations. Provides methods for starting the game, accessing board cells, getting suggestions, and checking game completion.
